  "title": "Part Time Kitchen Crew ($15/hour)",
  "description": "<p><strong>• Well Established Japanese F&amp;B Company</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Salary: $15/hour + Incentive</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Working Location: Islandwide</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Flexible Working Hours</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in the kitchen and food preparation.</li>\n  <li>Prepare equipment for the cooking process.</li>\n  <li>Weigh, measure and mix ingredients according to recipes.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a high standard of all food preparation and service in the kitchen according to the required standards.</li>\n  <li>Ensure accurate and consistent cook practice and presentation.</li>\n  <li>Ensure the kitchen areas are clean, tidy and organized.</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper hygiene practices based on Food &amp; Beverages Safety and Hygiene policies.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in controlling cost and minimize food wastages.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE N Level and above</li>\n  <li>1 - 3 years of relevant experiences in similar role</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
